<h2>AI tools for content creation</h2>
<p>Now, using<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/02/25/ai-content-generators"> AI tools to create your content</a> start to finish isnâ€™t the best strategy. Especially because it can impact your brandâ€™s<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/topical-authority"> authority</a> and relationship with your audience, but you should definitely use AI tools for productivity gains throughout the content creation processâ€”whether itâ€™s brainstorming, outlining, or even reviewing for tone. Just be sure to play an active role and review everything.</p>
<h3>1. Jasper</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.jasper.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jasper</a> is a generative AI tool that helps you create marketing copy, including <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2015/02/09/how-to-write-a-blog-post">blog posts</a>, product descriptions, landing pages, social captions, and more. This AI tool uses advanced large language models (LLMs) purpose-built for writing copy, which makes the output stronger than some other <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/chatgpt-alternatives">alternatives</a>. Plus, you can input examples so that Jasper learns your brand voice and can replicate it as it writes.</p>
<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-jasper.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Jasper" width="937" height="468" class="aligncenter wp-image-93206 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-jasper.webp 937w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-jasper-480x240.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 937px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.jasper.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>However, this better output comes with a cost. Jasper is pricier than a lot of other options, so make sure it works for your budget before testing it out.</p>
<p><strong>Jasper pricing:</strong> <a href="https://www.jasper.ai/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jasperâ€™s Creator plan</a> costs $39 per month.</p>
<h3><strong></strong>2. Copy.ai</h3>
<p><a href="http://copy.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Copy.ai</a> is an <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-copywriting-tools">AI copywriting assistant</a> that can produce nearly any type of copy, but it excels particularly in creating short-form content, such as <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/instagram-ad-copy">social captions</a>, product descriptions, and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/07/21/promotional-email-examples">marketing emails</a>. The tool is straightforward and easy to use, so you can get lots of options quickly.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-copy-ai.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Copy ai" width="873" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-93207 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-copy-ai.webp 873w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-copy-ai-480x330.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 873px, 100vw" /></p>
