<p>Whether youâ€™re growing a business account or your own personal brand, the industry youâ€™re targeting matters. <a href="https://www.socialpilot.co/blog/best-time-to-post-on-linkedin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Social Pilot</a> analyzed the engagement for more than 50,000 LinkedIn accounts to determine the best times to post on LinkedIn to reach people in your sector.</p>
