<p>With these capabilities, itâ€™s no wonder that experts expect AI to dominate video marketing trends in 2025. Simon HÃ¸iberg, the SaaS founder and YouTube personality, recently shared his confidence in AI videos on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/simonhoiberg_im-bullish-on-ai-videos-it-seems-like-ugcPost-7280567890292928513-dDuN/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
