										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Every day, billions of users are scrolling through thousands of posts on dozens of social media platforms. With this kind of excess, itâ€™s easy to feel defeated. How can a small business stand out with all this noise? Itâ€™s simple: By developing a targeted social media strategy.</p>
<p>With a social media strategy, youâ€™ll focus on reaching your audience with high-quality content they want to see on the platforms where theyâ€™re already spending time. You wonâ€™t be competing with all the noise for any attention; youâ€™ll be putting a plan in place to reach your potential customers. In this article, weâ€™ll go over all the steps you need to follow to create a social media strategy that works for your business.</p>
<h3>Contents</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="#what-is-a-social-media-strategy">What is a social media strategy?</a></li>
